<bibRefCitation author="Hernandez-Padilla" box="[248,595,1375,1401]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Hernandez-Padilla" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="863 - 865" refId="ref284893" refString="Hernandez-Padilla, J. C., Capetillo-Pinar, N., Aranceta-Garza, F., Yee-Duarte, J. A., Vele-Arellano, N. &amp; Velazquez-Abunader, I. (2020) Length-weight relationships of 12 marine fish species from the Pacific coast of Guatamala associated with smallscale fisheries. Journal of Applied Ichthyology, 36, 863 - 865. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / jai. 14093" type="journal article" year="2020">
Hernández-Padilla 
