<bibRefCitation author="De La Cruz-Aguero and Cota-Gomez" firstAuthor="De La Cruz-Aguero" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="353 - 358" refId="ref274171" refString="De La Cruz-Aguero, J. &amp; Cota-Gomez, V. M. (1998) Ichthyofauna of San Ignacio Lagoon, Baja California Sur, Mexico: new records and range extensions. Ciencias Marinas, 24, 353 - 358. https: // doi. org / 10.7773 / cm. v 24 i 3.751" type="journal article" year="1998">De La Cruz-Agüero and Cota-Gómez 1998</bibRefCitation>
